These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: cola, juice, lemonade, water
Cigar: siglo, swisher, ritmeester, bolivar
1. Beverage:cola is on the right of Cigar:ritmeester##1
2. Cigar:bolivar is on the far left##1
3. Cigar:ritmeester is between Cigar:swisher and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:water is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:lemonade is between Beverage:juice and Beverage:cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| Cigar      | bolivar | siglo | ritmeester   | swisher |

