.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Color: amber, ebony, emerald, lilac
Nationality: british, colombian, dutch, turkish
1. Nationality:turkish is between Color:emerald and Nationality:colombian##2
2. Color:lilac is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:dutch is on the right of Nationality:british##1
4. Color:amber is on the left of Nationality:british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Color         | ebony | amber | emerald | lilac |
| Nationality   | colombian    | turkish   | british | dutch       |

