2. Nationality:colombian is between Nationality:british and House:modern##2
3. Nationality:british is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:french is on the left of House:tower##1
5. House:modern == Nationality:french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| House          | cottage    | palace | modern   | tower  |
| Nationality   | british | colombian   | french | australian |

