3. Cigar:davidoff is on the far right##1
4. Pet:cat is on the right of Cigar:fonseca##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | rat   | cat    | pony       | lizard   |
| Cigar   | fonseca | aristoff | old-henry | davidoff |

